com.netflix.governator.spi

Interface LifecycleListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LifecycleListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLifecycleListener, JettyModule.JettyShutdown, LifecycleModule.LifecycleProvisionListener, LoggingProvisionMetricsLifecycleListener, SafeLifecycleListener, TestLifecycleListener

    public interface LifecycleListener
    Listener for Injector lifecycle events. When writing a LifecycleListener that is managed by Guice, make sure to inject all dependencies lazily using Provider injection. Otherwise, these dependencies will be instantiated too early thereby bypassing lifecycle features in LifecycleModule.
